Package net.minecraftforge.debug.client

Class ObjModelTest

java.lang.Object
net.minecraftforge.debug.client.ObjModelTest
public class ObjModelTest extends Object
Tests loading and rendering an obj-model using the using Forge's ObjLoader. When enabled, this will render a pyramid loaded from an obj model at coordinates 0,0,0.
